Author Id: 1257469301435400238
Avatar URL: assets\8286d5b1308e7b3d80a3523e4ec50548-C029D.png
Content: IF THERE IS A TAG THAT HAPPENS IN THIS CHANNEL, THIS MEANS THAT THERE IS A PHONE-BANK LIST THAT NEEDS CLICKING TO BE APPROVED!! VERY EASY STEPS:

1. Click the link!
2. Click the approve button, and continue holding down the enter/return key (on a laptop/desktop is best) to quickly click through your assigned numbers. 
3. Press 'approve another batch' to get another set of numbers to approve. 
4. Continue until there are no more numbers to approve!
--------------------

Content: When you open the link on a computer, click "Request Numbers". Manually click once on "Approve ID" for the first one. When the second one pops us, hold down the enter key and it will zoom through all 499 on the batch in under 50 seconds. üôÇ That's the fastest, easiest way! You do have to manually click the first number "approval" for each batch of 500, but then you can long hold the enter key to zoom through the 2nd through 500th! Then request a new batch and repeat until there are no more available. Or until you can't do it anymore.

Content: These phone numbers are used for phone banking. My understanding is that based on FTC law, there is a process that must be completed before these numbers can be used. Part of that process is manually approving each number. They can not be approved by automatic means. So, the campaign needs us volunteers to help with the approval process.

Author: Rich Holcombe (WI) (priven.)

Avatar URL: assets\63e48c9523aa87666c7f4d2b6d23a691-271FE.png
Content: You're approving numbers to be added.
When a link gets posted here:
- Open that link in an internet browser.
- Click on the blue box to begin processing numbers, they will be in batches of 500 (provided there is more than that to approve)
- You click the blue box to approve each one, you can also hold down the enter key to make this go faster.
- Keep doing this until you're done or the page tells you "No callees require approval at this time"
--------------------

--- Message ---
Message ID: 1283865930258055259
Message Type: Default
Reply to: None
Timestamp: 2024-09-12T19:04:50.849+00:00
Author: HeyYo210 (heyyo210)
Author Id: 1145369497834885270
Avatar URL: assets\7159b181ff0fc16f91cc03982ab5a069-FC46E.png
Content: I think I can actually answer this, I think üòÇ I worked in a market research call center managing sample for 2 decades. 
In many states using an automated dialer is illegal if you do not have a previous relationship with that person/phone number. So when making a call, until the household is reached and gives approval to be contacted in some way, the calls must be made manually. 
Once contact is made and some sort of relationship is establishing it is legal to use an automated dialer.
--------------------

Content: This one is fairly random but staff drops a link here, you open it, start click (accepting numbers). After the first number accepted, you can just hold down "enter" and zoom through 500. Then request a new batch. Continue until done. We've had some as many as 250K numbers and our awesome volunteers have clicked through within a very short time and approved them all. So you have to be FAST and online to catch them before they are gone. 

Also, no auto-clicker apps on this as that's against the law. Thank you!

Content: Yep! Join in the fun! This is approving lists for phonebanks. You essentially click the link that's provided here, and click a button to "accept" each specific caller (we don't get any data about them). It's a lot easier to do it on your computer, where you don't have to click each one separately.

We can only fundraise on behalf of: Democratic National Committee, Harris Victory Fund or Harris for President directly. 
We can recruit for "non-official events" that are hosted by partner organizations or volunteers in ‚Å†non-official-events-only. We can recruit into anything that is listed on events.democrats.org or a state democratic party's mobilize.
Rule 3 Note > Relevance: Do not post links to petitions or other calls to action that haven‚Äôt been approved by Staff. This forum is not intended for debates. Additionally, do not attempt to raise funds or share fundraising links for any entity besides the Democratic National Committee. Using this server to raise funds for yourself, another candidate, or another organization violates campaign finance law and is strictly prohibited. Anyone who violates the rules is subject to removal or time out.
When in doubt, ask @Community Moderator.

Content: HOW TO DO THIS:

NOTE: Computer is definitely best for this, but a phone or tablet works too (lots more effort though)

1. Click the link in the highlighted post. It will open a new page in your browser (Chrome, Firefox etc. Safari works, but not best choice.)

2. Click the button to start, AND THEN: 

IF COMPUTER:
3. Hold down the Enter key while it‚Äôs going through a list of 500 callers. 
NOTE: Due to Finance Campaign Rules, YOU CANNOT USE ANY TYPE OF AUTOMATION (program or physical device)

IF PHONE:
3. Click the ‚ÄúApprove ID‚Äù button 500 times. 

NEXT STEP FOR ALL DEVICES:
4. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNice Work! Keep approving assignments‚Äù ‚Äî> Return to Step 3 (Click for a new list)

5. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNo callees require approval at this time. Check again‚Äù ‚Äî> No more lists. Close the tab.

6. Yay you did it! Thanks for your help!

NOTE: Due to Finance Campaign Rules, YOU CANNOT USE ANY TYPE OF AUTOMATION (program or physical device), but you CAN physically weigh down your Enter key to not press it with your finger the whole time. Examples: stacked erasers, bolt with washer and nuts, clothespin, etc. SAFARI WON‚ÄôT LET YOU DO THIS. 

IF PHONE:

Message ID: 1297905916573782079
Message Type: Reply
Reply to: 1297905628664041565

Author: Steve (steve04145)
Author Id: 1282342719104225361
Avatar URL: assets\c82b3fa769ed6e6ffdea579381ed5f5c-FDA22.png
Content: HOW TO DO THIS:

NOTE: Computer is definitely best for this, but a phone or tablet works too (lots more effort though)

1. Click the link in the highlighted post. It will open a new page in your browser (Chrome, Firefox etc. Safari works, but not best choice.)

2. Click the button to start, AND THEN: 

IF COMPUTER:
3. Hold down the Enter key while it‚Äôs going through a list of 500 callers. 
NOTE: Due to Finance Campaign Rules, YOU CANNOT USE ANY TYPE OF AUTOMATION (program or physical device), but you CAN physically weigh down your Enter key to not press it with your finger the whole time. Examples: stacked erasers, bolt with washer and nuts, clothespin, etc. SAFARI WON‚ÄôT LET YOU DO THIS. 

IF PHONE:
3. Click the ‚ÄúApprove ID‚Äù button 500 times. 

NEXT STEP FOR ALL DEVICES:
4. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNice Work! Keep approving assignments‚Äù ‚Äî> Return to Step 3 (Click for a new list)

5. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNo callees require approval at this time. Check again‚Äù ‚Äî> No more lists. Close the tab.

6. Yay you did it! Thanks for your help!
--------------------

Content: HOW TO DO THIS:

NOTE: Computer is definitely best for this, but a phone or tablet works too (lots more effort though)

1. Click the link in the highlighted post. It will open a new page in your browser (Chrome, Firefox etc. Safari works, but not best choice.)

2. Click the button to start, AND THEN:

IF COMPUTER:
3. Hold down the Enter key while it‚Äôs going through a list of 500 callers.
NOTE: Due to Finance Campaign Rules, YOU CANNOT USE ANY TYPE OF AUTOMATION (program or physical device), but you CAN physically weigh down your Enter key to not press it with your finger the whole time. Examples: stacked erasers, bolt with washer and nuts, clothespin, etc. SAFARI WON‚ÄôT LET YOU DO THIS.

IF PHONE:
3. Click the ‚ÄúApprove ID‚Äù button 500 times.

NEXT STEP FOR ALL DEVICES:
4. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNice Work! Keep approving assignments‚Äù ‚Äî> Return to Step 3 (Click for a new list)

5. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNo callees require approval at this time. Check again‚Äù ‚Äî> No more lists. Close the tab.

6. Yay you did it! Thanks for your help!

Content: HOW TO DO THIS:

NOTE: Computer is definitely best for this, but a phone or tablet works too (lots more effort though)

1. Click the link in the highlighted post. It will open a new page in your browser (Chrome, Firefox etc. Safari works, but not best choice.)

2. Click the button to start, AND THEN: 

IF COMPUTER:
3. Hold down the Enter key while it‚Äôs going through a list of 500 callers. 
NOTE: Due to Finance Campaign Rules, YOU CANNOT USE ANY TYPE OF AUTOMATION (program or physical device), but you CAN physically weigh down your Enter key to not press it with your finger the whole time. Examples: stacked erasers, bolt with washer and nuts, clothespin, etc. SAFARI WON‚ÄôT LET YOU DO THIS. 

IF PHONE:
3. Click the ‚ÄúApprove ID‚Äù button 500 times. 

NEXT STEP FOR ALL DEVICES:
4. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNice Work! Keep approving assignments‚Äù ‚Äî> Return to Step 3 (Click for a new list)

5. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNo callees require approval at this time. Check again‚Äù ‚Äî> No more lists. Close the tab.

6. Yay you did it! Thanks for your help!

Content: HOW TO DO THIS:

NOTE: Computer is definitely best for this, but a phone or tablet works too (lots more effort though)

1. Click the link in the highlighted post. It will open a new page in your browser (Chrome, Firefox etc. Safari works, but not best choice.)

2. Click the button to start, AND THEN:

IF COMPUTER:
3. Hold down the Enter key while it‚Äôs going through a list of 500 callers.
NOTE: Due to Finance Campaign Rules, YOU CANNOT USE ANY TYPE OF AUTOMATION (program or physical device), but you CAN physically weigh down your Enter key to not press it with your finger the whole time. Examples: stacked erasers, bolt with washer and nuts, clothespin, etc. SAFARI WON‚ÄôT LET YOU DO THIS.

IF PHONE:
3. Click the ‚ÄúApprove ID‚Äù button 500 times.

NEXT STEP FOR ALL DEVICES:
4. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNice Work! Keep approving assignments‚Äù ‚Äî> Return to Step 3 (Click for a new list)

5. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNo callees require approval at this time. Check again‚Äù ‚Äî> No more lists. Close the tab.

6. Yay you did it! Thanks for your help!
--------------------

She said she had this conversation where she was aligned with a Black cab driver or something... and then at the end he shocks her and says he is voting for trump still.

Who benefits from you believing abc? 

Something like that

It is a sort of follow the money sort of question. Maybe if nothing else leave them with that thought

1. Click the link in the highlighted post. It will open a new page in your browser (Chrome, Firefox etc. Safari works, but not best choice.)

IF COMPUTER:
3. Hold down the Enter key while it‚Äôs going through a list of 500 callers. 
NOTE: Due to Finance Campaign Rules, YOU CANNOT USE ANY TYPE OF AUTOMATION (program or physical device), but you CAN physically weigh down your Enter key to not press it with your finger the whole time. Examples: stacked erasers, bolt with washer and nuts, clothespin, etc. SAFARI WON‚ÄôT LET YOU DO THIS. 

IF PHONE:
3. Click the ‚ÄúApprove ID‚Äù button 500 times.

Message ID: 1299610173270392842

Author Id: 465305140786888705
Avatar URL: assets\a187dcd150192cbe1a6b1b9cb0ffe55c-6C116.png
Content: HOW TO DO THIS:

NOTE: Computer is definitely best for this, but a phone or tablet works too (lots more effort though)

1. Click the link in the highlighted post. It will open a new page in your browser (Chrome, Firefox etc. Safari works, but not best choice.)

2. Click the button to start, AND THEN: 

IF COMPUTER:
3. Hold down the Enter key while it‚Äôs going through a list of 500 callers. 
NOTE: Due to Finance Campaign Rules, YOU CANNOT USE ANY TYPE OF AUTOMATION (program or physical device), but you CAN physically weigh down your Enter key to not press it with your finger the whole time. Examples: stacked erasers, bolt with washer and nuts, clothespin, etc. SAFARI WON‚ÄôT LET YOU DO THIS. 

IF PHONE:
3. Click the ‚ÄúApprove ID‚Äù button 500 times. 

NEXT STEP FOR ALL DEVICES:
4. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNice Work! Keep approving assignments‚Äù ‚Äî> Return to Step 3 (Click for a new list)

5. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNo callees require approval at this time. Check again‚Äù ‚Äî> No more lists. Close the tab.

6. Yay you did it! Thanks for your help!
--------------------

Content: If there are any newbies joining us today:

HOW TO DO THIS:

NOTE: Computer is definitely best for this, but a phone or tablet works too (lots more effort though)

1. Click the link in the highlighted post. It will open a new page in your browser (Chrome, Firefox etc. Safari works, but not best choice.)

2. Click the button to start, AND THEN:

IF COMPUTER (fastest option by far!):
3. Hold down the Enter key while it‚Äôs going through a list of 500 callers.
NOTE: Due to Finance Campaign Rules, YOU CANNOT USE ANY TYPE OF AUTOMATION (program or physical device), but you CAN physically weigh down your Enter key to not press it with your finger the whole time. Examples: stacked erasers, bolt with washer and nuts, clothespin, etc. SAFARI WON‚ÄôT LET YOU DO THIS.

IF PHONE:
3. Click the ‚ÄúApprove ID‚Äù button 500 times.

NEXT STEP FOR ALL DEVICES:
4. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNice Work! Keep approving assignments‚Äù ‚Äî> Return to Step 3 (Click for a new list)

5. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNo callees require approval at this time. Check again‚Äù ‚Äî> No more lists. Close the tab.

6. Yay you did it! Thanks for your help!

Content: HOW TO DO THIS:

NOTE: Computer is definitely best for this, but a phone or tablet works too (lots more effort though)

1. Click the link in the highlighted post. It will open a new page in your browser (Chrome, Firefox etc. Safari works, but not best choice.)

2. Click the button to start, AND THEN: 

IF COMPUTER:
3. Hold down the Enter key while it‚Äôs going through a list of 500 callers. 
NOTE: Due to Finance Campaign Rules, YOU CANNOT USE ANY TYPE OF AUTOMATION (program or physical device), but you CAN physically weigh down your Enter key to not press it with your finger the whole time. Examples: stacked erasers, bolt with washer and nuts, clothespin, etc. SAFARI WON‚ÄôT LET YOU DO THIS. 

IF PHONE:
3. Click the ‚ÄúApprove ID‚Äù button 500 times. 

NEXT STEP FOR ALL DEVICES:
4. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNice Work! Keep approving assignments‚Äù ‚Äî> Return to Step 3 (Click for a new list)

5. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNo callees require approval at this time. Check again‚Äù ‚Äî> No more lists. Close the tab.

6. Yay you did it! Thanks for your help!

NOTE: Computer is definitely best for this, but a phone or tablet works too (lots more effort though)

1. Click the link in the highlighted post. It will open a new page in your browser (Chrome, Firefox etc. Safari works, but not best choice.)

IF COMPUTER:
3. Hold down the Enter key while it‚Äôs going through a list of 500 callers. 
NOTE: Due to Finance Campaign Rules, YOU CANNOT USE ANY TYPE OF AUTOMATION (program or physical device), but you CAN physically weigh down your Enter key to not press it with your finger the whole time. Examples: stacked erasers, bolt with washer and nuts, clothespin, etc. SAFARI WON‚ÄôT LET YOU DO THIS. 

IF PHONE:
3. Click the ‚ÄúApprove ID‚Äù button 500 times. 

NEXT STEP FOR ALL DEVICES:
4. IF IT SHOWS: ‚ÄúNice Work! Keep approving assignments‚Äù ‚Äî> Return to Step 3 (Click for a new list)

6. Yay you did it! Thanks for your help!
